<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_05_SU_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema616_09 (2).css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_05_su_0005" data-current-page="page_1, page_2, page_3">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y">부피가 1 ㎤인 쌓기나무로 부피가 1 ㎥인 정육면체를 만들어 1 ㎥와 1 ㎤의 관계를 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">부피가 1 ㎥인 정육면체를 만들 때 한 모서리에 쌓을 수 있는 쌓기나무는 몇 개인가요?</h3>
          <div class="flex align_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_09_SU/616_05_004.png" alt="" />
              <div class="unit_a">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_b">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_c">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_d">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_e">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_f">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_g">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_h">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_i">1 ㎝</div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap answer1">
              <math-field data-answer-single="100"></math-field>
              <span>개</span>
            </div>
            <div class="subimg">
              <!-- 버튼 클릭시 말풍선 나오는 걸로 변경 -->
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_09_SU/bubble1.png" alt="" />
              <div class="bubble">
                <p lang="y">1 m는 100 ㎝야.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 1page -->

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">부피가 1 ㎥인 정육면체를 만드는 데 필요한 쌓기나무는 모두 몇 개인가요?</h3>
          <div class="flex align_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_09_SU/616_05_004.png" alt="" />
              <div class="unit_a">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_b">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_c">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_d">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_e">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_f">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_g">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_h">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_i">1 ㎝</div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap answer1">
              <math-field data-answer-single="1000000"></math-field>
              <span>개</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 2page -->

        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3 lang="y">1 ㎥는 몇 ㎤인지 알아보세요.</h3>
          <div class="flex align_center">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_09_SU/616_05_004.png" alt="" />
              <div class="unit_a">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_b">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_c">100 m</div>
              <div class="unit_d">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_e">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_f">1 m</div>
              <div class="unit_g">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_h">1 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_i">1 ㎝</div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap answer2">
              <span>1 ㎥=</span>
              <math-field data-answer-single="1000000"></math-field>
              <span>㎤</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row_area">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_09_SU/row_box.png" alt="" />
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 3page -->
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">확인</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
